Package: signnet
Title: Methods to Analyse Signed Networks
Version: 0.5.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "David",
           family = "Schoch",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "david.schoch@manchester.ac.uk")
Description: The package is designed for the analysis of signed networks. This includes several measures to check for structural balance, blockmodeling algorithms, centrality and projections of signed two-mode networks.
Depends: R (>= 3.2.0)
URL: https://github.com/schochastics/signnet
BugReports: https://github.com/schochastics/signnet/issues
